collectible.name: SketchPoetic Heal Coin (Gold)
collectible.description:
This NFT will be gifted to collectors, curators, creators who elevate art as a tool for healing and advocates for holistic health, i.e. mind, body, spirit. This coin will serve as a connective thread across a Healing Collective and support the onboarding of new community members passionate about Creative Expression & Mental Health.
For 2021 Inaugural Edition of the Heal Coin, there will only be 111 minted. These editions will be gifted or distributed through giveaways by Sheila Darcey, Founder of SketchPoetic.
As the value of the Healing Collective rises, so will the value of this NFT.

Concept by Sheila Darcey Designed by SuiLuv

collectible.name: Love - Venice
collectible.description: When we say that Venice is the land of Love, we are not mistaken. Love has lived in Venice for many years, and everyone sees it passing by, some manage to talk to it, but it never stays in the same place for long. But it was Love that made SELF fall in love with TERA. And it is Love that will drive this story.
